Classes
Class
Description
AppDriver
The `AppDriver` class is responsible for sorting an array of three-dimensional shapes based on user-defined criteria.
CompareArea
The CompareArea class is a custom comparator for comparing objects of the ThreeDimensionalShape class based on their surface areas.
CompareHeight
The CompareHeight class is a custom comparator for comparing objects of the ThreeDimensionalShape class based on their heights.
CompareVolume
The CompareVolume class is a custom comparator for comparing objects of the ThreeDimensionalShape class based on their volumes.
Cone
A class representing a three-dimensional cone shape.

A class representing a three-dimensional cylinder shape.
FileReader
The FileReader class reads three-dimensional shape data from a file and creates an array of shapes.

Pyramid
A class representing a three-dimensional pyramid shape.
SquarePrism
A class representing a three-dimensional square prism shape.

An abstract class representing a three-dimensional shape.
TriangularPrism
A class representing a three-dimensional triangular prism shape.
Utility<T>
The Utility class provides a collection of sorting algorithms and utility methods for sorting arrays of generic types.
